    # "And Sarah was eager to give it to them."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2d352c88 (line 59475)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2d352c88:
    # "She saw how her commands were relayed and her army sprung to life."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5bad20d4 (line 59476)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5bad20d4:
    # "The flanks on each far end of her army began to move forward."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_106c482b (line 59477)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_106c482b:
    # "Wrapping around the center, they closed off the only escape that had been available to the Tribesmen."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8f395316 (line 59478)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8f395316:
    # "Sarah watched as less then a few dozen Tribesmen realized what was happening and managed to escape the encirclement."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c24a5d60 (line 59479)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c24a5d60:
    # "The others, too lost in the frenzy of battle, did not retreat."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_66b25dd3 (line 59480)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_66b25dd3:
    # "The flanking units, mostly spearmen, had not yet seen battle and were eager for it."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_be01bdef (line 59481)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_be01bdef:
    # "Attacking the Tribesmen from behind, they found easy targets that were exhausted and caught by surprise."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_12230053 (line 59482)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_12230053:
    # "With heavy shields and long spears, even the common Rosannan footsoldier found it easy to kill these sons of war."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_23c3f9d4 (line 59483)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_23c3f9d4:
    # "Pressed on all sides, surrounded, the Tribesmen continued to fight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d73765ea (line 59484)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d73765ea:
    # "But their position had deteriorated so quickly that even they struggled to adapt."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b7a686b1 (line 59485)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b7a686b1:
    # "While each of them was reduced to fighting as a single warrior, her army moved as one."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_89ea3575 (line 59486)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_89ea3575:
    # "The advancing Rosannan army pushed the Tribesmen together from all sides."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1f3599fc (line 59487)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1f3599fc:
    # "Their great advantage, their horses, turned meaningless in the frenzy of such a close melee."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_804c2c78 (line 59488)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_804c2c78:
    # "Sarah smiled as she saw the core of the Tribesmen formation shrink."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_de483ad3 (line 59489)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_de483ad3:
    # "One by one, layer by layer, her army took the Tribesmen forces apart."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d723f53e (line 59490)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d723f53e:
    # "They had gambled a lot on the hope that they might kill her and break apart her army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8eaa8c4c (line 59491)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8eaa8c4c:
    # "But they had fallen short."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3c20276e (line 59492)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3c20276e:
    # "And in war, there was no partial victory."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4c5e3335 (line 59493)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4c5e3335:
    # s "You!"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4f3d3296 (line 59494)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4f3d3296:
    # "Sarah called another messenger over."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_17b9a584 (line 59495)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_17b9a584:
    # s "Report along the line, finish up the last of the Tribesmen, then reposition to move on the capital."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6c292580 (line 59496)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6c292580:
    # s "Also, instruct the engineers to keep firing, I want to see the city wall crumble."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_3225bf19 (line 59497)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3225bf19:
    # "Scout" "Yes, Commander!"
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_06fe8448 (line 59498)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_06fe8448:
    # "The young man rushed off along the length of the line, spreading her instructions as fast as he could manage."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2a5de8ed (line 59499)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2a5de8ed:
    # "In little time at all, the last of the Tribesmen were put to death."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e376c101 (line 59500)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e376c101:
    # "Once the victory had become clear, a mad zeal seemed to spread through the formation."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_fa2c973d (line 59501)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fa2c973d:
    # "No longer were they hesitant for war. They were hungry for it."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4a7abaa1 (line 59502)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4a7abaa1:
    # "Sarah heard them sing out their battle songs in eager anticipation for marching on the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_38b8d922 (line 59503)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_38b8d922:
    # "They had feared the Tribesmen, as well they should have, but now they learned they were as mortal as any other man."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_47e002d1 (line 59504)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_47e002d1:
    # "They could be broken."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_506fe120 (line 59505)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_506fe120:
    # "Sarah watched her army fall back into formation."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5ccb6482 (line 59506)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5ccb6482:
    # "Overhead, she saw the boulders of the trebuchets, flying across the sky, striking the outer walls of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0d296b0e (line 59507)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0d296b0e:
    # "Larges plumes of dust rose up."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e580b870 (line 59508)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e580b870:
    # "Stones, scattering, walls breaking, the violent roar of the siege."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_88fdccf4 (line 59509)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_88fdccf4:
    # "Sarah looked at one of her officers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_701c967e (line 59510)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_701c967e:
    # s "What is the situation with the Tribesmen?"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2dd4c097 (line 59511)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2dd4c097:
    # "Officer" "This attack was a large portion of their forces, but it wasn't all of them."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c49ae365 (line 59512)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c49ae365:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_546dc23d (line 59513)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_546dc23d:
    # s "How many remain?"
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f9dd035d (line 59514)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f9dd035d:
    # "Officer" "Hard to say, they're hiding behind their walls."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c71bf744 (line 59515)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c71bf744:
    # "Officer" "Best estimate, maybe less than five-thousand."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_15cb7601 (line 59516)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_15cb7601:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f611c8a7 (line 59517)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f611c8a7:
    # "A sizeable force, but far fewer than she had in her own army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7ca0daa7 (line 59518)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7ca0daa7:
    # "Still, when she moved into the city, it would be a brutal slog."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_18076e9b (line 59519)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_18076e9b:
    # "Block-by-block, she would have to fight her way through the city. Attacks could come from any direction."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_800e88a8 (line 59520)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_800e88a8:
    # "And the march to Castle Reinmeer was long."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_08035ec0 (line 59521)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_08035ec0:
    # "Then there was the Castle itself, no easy target itself."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c5a5073f (line 59522)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c5a5073f:
    # "Still, it had to be done."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_40c64329 (line 59523)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40c64329:
    # "Sarah watched the walls of the city until finally a large boulder struck true."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2e666d99 (line 59524)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2e666d99:
    # "The integrity of the entire length of the wall gave out all at once."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5d5bebbd (line 59525)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5d5bebbd:
    # "Along the rest of the wall, Sarah saw other gaps emerge. Even the city gate seemed close to collapsing."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8cb993fe (line 59532)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8cb993fe:
    # "Sarah grabbed the horn that was tied to her waist."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_884f073f (line 59533)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_884f073f:
    # "She drew in as much air as she could, filling her lungs, and brought the horn to her lips."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_12716d15 (line 59534)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_12716d15:
    # "Exhaling with great force, she let out a titanous blast from the horn."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ad6fe66c (line 59535)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ad6fe66c:
    # "The deep, pounding sound seemed to reverberate into her bones."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ff05a0bc (line 59536)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ff05a0bc:
    # "All at once, her army began to march, advancing on the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1a7990df (line 59537)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1a7990df:
    # "Sarah lowered the horn and watched in awe at the sheer size of her army."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_9b84f742 (line 59538)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9b84f742:
    # "Remaining near the rear, she advanced along with her army, staying wary of any other surprise attacks."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bb80c6dd (line 59539)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bb80c6dd:
    # "Her army could win the battle, but if she died the blow to morale could undo much of their advantage."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5c4a8aeb (line 59540)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5c4a8aeb:
    # "She didn't enjoy letting others risk their lives on her account, but she also knew she wasn't just one person anymore."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5c1928c5 (line 59541)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5c1928c5:
    # "Looking upon her home, she knew she was becoming so much more."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_305459ad (line 59542)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_305459ad:
    # "The army crossed the field."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_092d9673 (line 59543)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_092d9673:
    # "A few arrows fell on them as they advanced, but the large volley she had expected did not come."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1f25096f (line 59544)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1f25096f:
    # "The Tribesmen were experienced in war, but sieges were something they had far less experience with."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_9efe6bf4 (line 59545)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9efe6bf4:
    # "Least of all, defending from a siege."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_fffc6bd2 (line 59546)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fffc6bd2:
    # "It was then perhaps no surprise they had failed to prepare as well as they could have."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2be0ed21 (line 59547)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2be0ed21:
    # "As they neared the walls of the city, the gaps were large enough for her soldiers to advance safely."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4c3ce0ed (line 59554)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4c3ce0ed:
    # "Her army moved into the city, passing through the damaged sections of the wall."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_90b27b27 (line 59555)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_90b27b27:
    # "They were hardly more than a few steps in when the Tribesmen began their attack."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_66a73d63 (line 59556)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_66a73d63:
    # "Using the narrow streets of the capital to their advantage, they hoped to compensate for their smaller numbers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e91011e5 (line 59557)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e91011e5:
    # "Arrows, shot from windows and rooftops."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6bcbefd8 (line 59558)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6bcbefd8:
    # "Small groups, carrying out cavalry charges, hitting and running, only to dissapear in some side-street."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2cb526d2 (line 59559)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2cb526d2:
    # "They were trying to bleed her army out."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ef3da89c (line 59560)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ef3da89c:
    # "But on her orders, her army kept advancing."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_afe000ab (line 59561)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_afe000ab:
    # "Sarah knew that with her numbers, her advantage was too significant."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ef564ac3 (line 59562)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ef564ac3:
    # "And so, despite the ongoing attacks from the Tribesmen, her army advanced deeper and deeper into the capital."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d0560bfd (line 59563)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d0560bfd:
    # "As they all slowly passed through the broken walls, the streets of the city began to swell with soldiers."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d58a1689 (line 59564)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d58a1689:
    # "Where at first the Tribesmen had been able to attack and dissapear into small streets, now Sarah's soldiers covered every angle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_7b36decf (line 59565)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7b36decf:
    # "More and more of them flooded every part of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_82bbb055 (line 59566)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_82bbb055:
    # "And with each street and square lost, the Tribesmen were pushed back into a smaller part of the city."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_0e0cfb12 (line 59567)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0e0cfb12:
    # "Already, Sarah could hear the cries of joy from the citizens, locked in their houses."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_cb172b05 (line 59568)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_cb172b05:
    # "As the Tribesmen lost ground, they found themselves increasingly concentrated into smaller and smaller spaces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c315719f (line 59569)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c315719f:
    # "Their hit-and-run tactics were increasingly becoming futile."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f202bd19 (line 59570)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f202bd19:
    # "When they did attack now, they did so in larger numbers. More regular fighting."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_316a1185 (line 59571)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_316a1185:
    # "But that kind of fighting took its toll."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a2d579f8 (line 59572)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a2d579f8:
    # "It took its toll on both sides, but the Tribesmen did not have the numbers to spare for such a grinding conflict."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_06d998e8 (line 59573)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_06d998e8:
    # "Sarah watched as their numbers dwindled."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f2c153ed (line 59574)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f2c153ed:
    # "How with each passing moment, the Tribesmen fell back further, surrendering more ground."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_68f3081e (line 59575)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_68f3081e:
    # "By now, most of the city had been liberated."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bbb97b75 (line 59576)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bbb97b75:
    # "And the only place to fall back to for the Tribesmen, was the Castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_37e0d0b8 (line 59577)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_37e0d0b8:
    # "Sarah pressed her forces on, giving pursuit to the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a93e783e (line 59578)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a93e783e:
    # "Finally, they relented and retreated all the way into the castle proper."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4683b96e (line 59579)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4683b96e:
    # "Letting the gate fall shut behind them, they withdrew to their last and final position."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bffb023d (line 59580)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bffb023d:
    # "Sarah watched as their haggard forces tried to set up their last defense."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2483e994 (line 59581)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2483e994:
    # "Her own forces had been wounded, but for the most part, her army was still plenty able to keep on the fight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_57824239 (line 59582)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_57824239:
    # "It was the Tribesmen that had ran out of steam."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_916ff36b (line 59583)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_916ff36b:
    # "The central road of the city that led up to the Castle was the most direct route of attack."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_9eb7b996 (line 59584)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9eb7b996:
    # "It would also be the quickest way to end this."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6c737298 (line 59585)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6c737298:
    # s "Send up the vanguard, have them take the castle gates. Once they're open, move up the rest of our forces."
    s ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5db669a5 (line 59586)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5db669a5:
    # "As ordered, Sarah watched her vanguard unit advance on the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d4e9cbf8 (line 59587)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d4e9cbf8:
    # "The vanguard consisted of the best soldiers from her mercenary company and Rosannan Knights that had survived The Fall."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_731aa96c (line 59588)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_731aa96c:
    # "Her most experienced soldiers, they would make for more than a decent match to the Tribesmen."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_5f97fc30 (line 59589)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5f97fc30:
    # "As they moved on the castle gates, the Tribesmen tried to stop their advance by firing arrows."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1ac8f27c (line 59590)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1ac8f27c:
    # "But the heavy plated armor and large shields of the vanguard unit meant that not a single arrow found purchase."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e00ff4d7 (line 59591)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e00ff4d7:
    # "Reaching the castle gates, they brought out their siege axes and got to work."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_9f2c0a42 (line 59592)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9f2c0a42:
    # "With each swing, they chipped away at the large, solid wood door that blocked the entrance into the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e9101096 (line 59593)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e9101096:
    # "The gates of Castle Reinmeer were solid, but even they could not endure forever."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_d0241088 (line 59594)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d0241088:
    # "Meanwhile, so close to the gate, the Tribesmen could no longer properly fire their arrows, leaving the vanguard to hack away."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c65556a8 (line 59595)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c65556a8:
    # "Eventually, Sarah saw the door splinter."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_707adfc1 (line 59596)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_707adfc1:
    # "A hole, large enough for maybe two men to move through."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_b0ec075b (line 59597)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b0ec075b:
    # "Without wasting a moment, they did."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_35b987a8 (line 59598)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_35b987a8:
    # "On the other side, they found the Tribesmen waiting for them, attacking as they tried to move through."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4888ddbc (line 59599)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4888ddbc:
    # "At first, the vanguard struggled, but with each man that moved through, they were able to push the Tribesmen back further."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_81c6ffa0 (line 59600)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_81c6ffa0:
    # "Before long, they had secured their position on the other end of the door and pushed the Tribesmen back into the Castle square."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_71ffb979 (line 59601)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_71ffb979:
    # "Rather than advance further, the vanguard seized the Castle gate."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_280e3e69 (line 59602)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_280e3e69:
    # "Pulling on the winch, they activated the machinery that had held the gates closed."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_8fec3250 (line 59603)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8fec3250:
    # "They swung open with a deep and heavy thud."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_2c28c22a (line 59604)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2c28c22a:
    # "Sarah heard her own army scream out in celebration as they saw that the final obstacle to their victory had been thrown open."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_ed320709 (line 59605)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ed320709:
    # "Before she could even issue the command, she saw her soldiers running up the road towards the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_f880afee (line 59606)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f880afee:
    # "Each was eager not to be denied their share of the glory of this day."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c3609386 (line 59607)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c3609386:
    # "The vanguard fell back, allowing the core of the army to move into the castle."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_41f6f59b (line 59608)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_41f6f59b:
    # "The Tribesmen fought bravely, but their numbers had dwindled so far that they could no longer mount a proper defense."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_1991f40c (line 59609)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1991f40c:
    # "Sarah's forces moved through the castle like a torrential surge, pushing through the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6939e86d (line 59610)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6939e86d:
    # "It was a battle for only a moment. Then it was a slaughter."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_86a184aa (line 59617)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_86a184aa:
    # "Sarah entered the castle when most of the fighting had been settled."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_4b291a40 (line 59618)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4b291a40:
    # "All about, she saw the bodies of the Tribesmen sprawled. Hacked up. Blood smeared."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_6620366a (line 59619)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6620366a:
    # "Here and there, some of her own soldiers were being treated for injuries of their own."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_c1f73f9d (line 59620)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c1f73f9d:
    # "A loud cheer rose up from the soldiers as they watched Sarah enter the castle grounds."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_e41eda09 (line 59621)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e41eda09:
    # "She raised her own fist in the air, triumphant."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_a9dd81d4 (line 59622)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a9dd81d4:
    # "She felt her own heart pounding in her chest at the sight."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_9242a94f (line 59623)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9242a94f:
    # "As her eyes fell on her ancestral home, the memories flooded back to her."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_57879a65 (line 59624)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_57879a65:
    # "And she was caught for a brief moment by a feeling she had lost for years."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_067bb6b1 (line 59625)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_067bb6b1:
    # "Home."
    ""

# WarriorQueen7Capital_bb1c330d (line 59626)
translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bb1c330d:
